        zh: '- 表示人生方向的困惑、缺乏目标或重要选择的犹豫\n- 思考：您在生活的哪个领域感到迷失？需要做出什么重要决定吗？',
        en: '- Indicates confusion about life direction, lack of goals, or hesitation about important choices\n- Reflect: In which area of life do you feel lost? Are there important decisions you need to make?'
      },
      {
        keywords: ['房子', '家', 'house', 'home', '房屋', '住宅'],
        zh: '- 房子代表自我和内在世界，不同房间反映人格的不同面向\n- 思考：房子的状态如何？您在房子里感觉如何？这可能反映您对自己的感受',
        en: '- Houses represent self and inner world; different rooms reflect different aspects of personality\n- Reflect: What was the condition of the house? How did you feel in it? This may reflect how you feel about yourself'
      },
      {
        keywords: ['亲人', '家人', '父母', '母亲', '父亲', 'parent', 'mother', 'father', 'family'],
        zh: '- 可能反映您与家人的关系，或是对亲情的渴望和思念\n- 思考：梦中的家人表现如何？这可能反映您对这些关系的潜在感受',
        en: '- May reflect your relationships with family or desires and longing for familial connections\n- Reflect: How did family members behave in the dream? This may reflect your underlying feelings about these relationships'
      },
      {
        keywords: ['工作', '老板', '同事', 'work', 'boss', 'colleague', '办公室', 'office'],
        zh: '- 可能与职场压力、工作表现或职业发展有关\n- 思考：您对当前的工作状态满意吗？有什么职业上的焦虑或期望？',
        en: '- May relate to workplace stress, work performance, or career development\n- Reflect: Are you satisfied with your current work situation? Do you have any career anxieties or expectations?'
      }
    ];

    let foundPatterns = false;
    for (const pattern of patterns) {
      const hasMatch = pattern.keywords.some(keyword => 
        dreamLower.includes(keyword.toLowerCase()) || dream.includes(keyword)
      );
      if (hasMatch) {
        insights += (isChinese ? pattern.zh : pattern.en) + '\n';
        foundPatterns = true;
      }
    }

    // Default insight if no patterns matched
    if (!foundPatterns) {
      insights = isChinese
        ? '- 梦境反映了您当前的心理状态和生活经验\n- 注意梦中的情绪和感受，它们往往是重要的线索\n- 梦境可能揭示您尚未意识到的需求或愿望\n- 建议：记录梦境的细节，包括人物、场景、情绪和感受，有助于深入理解'
        : '- Dreams reflect your current psychological state and life experiences\n- Pay attention to emotions and feelings in the dream, as they are often important clues\n- Dreams may reveal needs or desires you haven\'t yet consciously recognized\n- Suggestion: Record dream details including characters, scenes, emotions, and feelings to deepen understanding';
    }

    return insights;
  }
